<p>The <code>flex-wrap</code> utility controls whether flex items are
forced onto a single line or can wrap onto multiple lines, and if
wrapping occurs, in which direction.</p>
<p>By default, flex items will <strong>not wrap</strong> and try to fit
in a single row.</p>
